Package timetabler.entities

Class Summary
Course Holds all the information about course.
Lecture Holds information about lecture, such as its teacher, day, time from and time to, list of rooms and pointer to parent course.
Room Holds information about room.
Seminar Holds information about seminar, such as its teacher, day, time from and time to, list of rooms and pointer to parent course.
Teacher Holds information about teacher.
 

Enum Summary
Days Used to represent a day of week as a parameter in Lecture and Seminar objects.
